cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper is about object detection in images and involves training a model to predict properties of objects based on their appearance. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses a technique for improving the accuracy and efficiency of object detectors through machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper involves developing a model to make predictions based on visual data. 
4. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves processing and analyzing natural language descriptions of objects. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with analyzing and processing visual data.
